cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DL, cs.CR 

The paper discusses the evaluation and optimization of ontological queries, which are related to databases and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Databases), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). The paper also mentions description logics, which fall under cs.DL (Digital Libraries) and constraint rewriting, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
